{"nodes": [{"id": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_native_websocket", "label": "Native WebSocket over SignalR Decision", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "SignalR a\u00f1ade overhead de negociaci\u00f3n HTTP, fallback a long-polling, y serializaci\u00f3n JSON autom\u00e1tica que no es necesaria. WebSocket nativo da control total sobre el ciclo de vida de la conexi\u00f3n, formato de payload binario/texto, y minimiza latencia. El doc de arquitectura expl\u00edcitamente recomienda evitar SignalR."}, {"id": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_jpeg_binary_payload", "label": "JPEG Binary Upload + JSON Minified Response Format", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Enviar JPEG binario en lugar de Base64 reduce el payload ~33%. La respuesta JSON es m\u00ednima: solo 6 puntos de pose + expresi\u00f3n facial + visibilidad. Se eligi\u00f3 que el servidor devuelva coordenadas normalizadas (0-1) en lugar de \u00e1ngulos precalculados para mantener el servidor stateless y permitir que el cliente aplique calibraci\u00f3n y espejo."}, {"id": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_client_side_pipeline", "label": "Client-Side Transform Pipeline (Mirror + Angles + Lerp)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Toda la l\u00f3gica de transformaci\u00f3n (espejo, \u00e1ngulos, calibraci\u00f3n, Lerp) corre en C# en Blazor. El servidor solo hace inferencia de MediaPipe. Pipeline: Landmarks crudos \u2192 Calibraci\u00f3n (restar offset) \u2192 Espejo (X = 1.0 - X) \u2192 \u00c1ngulos (Atan2) \u2192 Lerp \u2192 CSS transform. Mantiene el servidor Python simple y stateless."}, {"id": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_component_layout", "label": "3-Column Grid Blazor Component Layout", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Layout grid 3 columnas (20%-60%-20%) con componentes Razor independientes: CameraPanel (izq, 20%), AvatarRenderer con Torso/Head/Arm (centro, 60%), CustomizationPanel (der, 20%). Servicios: AvatarState (Singleton), TrackingService (Scoped), CameraService (JS interop)."}, {"id": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_css_3d_torso", "label": "CSS 3D Torso Rotation with Clamping", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Contenedor .body-wrapper recibe transform: rotateY(angulo) calculado a partir de diferencia de profundidad (Z) entre hombros. \u00c1ngulo limitado a \u00b130\u00b0 con factor de sensibilidad bajo (~0.5). Contenedor central con perspective: 800px. Sin clamping, diferencias grandes producir\u00edan rotaciones no naturales."}, {"id": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_lerp_smoothing", "label": "Lerp Interpolation Smoothing (t=0.3)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Interpolaci\u00f3n lineal entre valor actual y objetivo con factor t=0.3 (30% hacia el target por frame). Buen balance entre respuesta r\u00e1pida y eliminaci\u00f3n de jitter. Valores menores (0.1) se sienten pesados, valores mayores (0.8) no filtran suficiente. Se aplica a todos los \u00e1ngulos: hombros, codos, torso y cabeza."}, {"id": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_calibration_offset", "label": "Client-Side Calibration Offset System", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Bot\u00f3n Calibrar captura 2 segundos de landmarks (60 frames a 30 FPS), calcula promedios, y los guarda como CalibrationOffset en el cliente. Los offsets se restan de cada landmark entrante antes de calcular \u00e1ngulos. Hacer la calibraci\u00f3n en el cliente mantiene el servidor stateless. Cada usuario tiene su propio offset."}, {"id": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_heartbeat_reconnection", "label": "Heartbeat + Exponential Backoff Reconnection Protocol", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Ping/pong cada 5s con timeout de 3s. Backoff exponencial: 1s \u2192 2s \u2192 4s \u2192 8s \u2192 16s max. Tras 5 intentos fallidos mostrar toast 'Conexi\u00f3n perdida'. Throttling adaptativo: RTT >100ms \u2192 20 FPS, >200ms \u2192 15 FPS, <50ms \u2192 30 FPS. Cr\u00edtico en WiFi de expo congestionada."}, {"id": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_wss_https", "label": "WSS/HTTPS Security for Production", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "En desarrollo usar ws://localhost:8765 y http://localhost:5000. En producci\u00f3n/expo configurar certificado autofirmado y usar wss:// y https://. getUserMedia solo funciona en contextos seguros. Para demo en red local, certificado autofirmado es suficiente."}, {"id": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_fallback_demo_mode", "label": "Fallback Demo Mode Without Camera", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Si getUserMedia falla o el usuario rechaza permisos, el sistema entra en modo demo: avatar en posici\u00f3n neutra, sliders manuales del panel izquierdo permiten simular movimiento. Panel de personalizaci\u00f3n sigue 100% funcional. No se debe mostrar una pantalla rota o vac\u00eda."}, {"id": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_avatarstate_singleton", "label": "AvatarState Singleton with OnChange Event Pattern", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "AvatarState.cs registrado como Singleton en DI de Blazor WASM. Expone propiedades (ShirtStyle, HatStyle, GlassesStyle, etc.) y evento OnChange. Los componentes se suscriben y re-renderizan al cambiar el estado. Singleton asegura estado compartido; patr\u00f3n event-based evita acoplar componentes entre s\u00ed."}, {"id": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_tailwind_css", "label": "Tailwind CDN + Native CSS Strategy", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Tailwind CDN en index.html para layout, utilidades y colores de la paleta (principal: #990066, textoBeige, fondoApp: #1a1a1a, fondoCentral: #2a2a35). CSS nativo en archivos .css por componente para transformaciones 3D y reglas complejas (sombras, keyframes, pseudo-elementos)."}], "edges": [{"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_native_websocket", "target": "websocket_tracking_spec_capability", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_jpeg_binary_payload", "target": "camera_capture_spec_capability", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_jpeg_binary_payload", "target": "websocket_tracking_spec_capability", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_client_side_pipeline", "target": "avatar_rendering_spec_capability", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_css_3d_torso", "target": "avatar_rendering_spec_capability", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_lerp_smoothing", "target": "movement_smoothing_spec_capability", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_calibration_offset", "target": "user_calibration_spec_capability", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_heartbeat_reconnection", "target": "connection_resilience_spec_capability", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_wss_https", "target": "connection_resilience_spec_capability", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_fallback_demo_mode", "target": "connection_resilience_spec_capability", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_avatarstate_singleton", "target": "avatar_customization_spec_capability", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_component_layout", "target": "avatar_rendering_spec_capability", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.85, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_tailwind_css", "target": "avatar_rendering_spec_capability", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.75, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_client_side_pipeline", "target": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_lerp_smoothing", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_client_side_pipeline", "target": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_calibration_offset", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_client_side_pipeline", "target": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_css_3d_torso", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_native_websocket", "target": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_jpeg_binary_payload", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_native_websocket", "target": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_heartbeat_reconnection", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.95, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_fallback_demo_mode", "target": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_avatarstate_singleton", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.85, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_heartbeat_reconnection", "target": "websocket_tracking_spec_capability", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.95, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}], "hyperedges": [{"id": "build_avatar_tracking_architecture_decisions", "label": "Foundational Architecture Decisions for Avatar Tracking System", "nodes": ["2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_native_websocket", "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_jpeg_binary_payload", "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_client_side_pipeline", "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_component_layout", "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_css_3d_torso", "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_lerp_smoothing", "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_calibration_offset", "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_heartbeat_reconnection", "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_wss_https", "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_fallback_demo_mode", "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_avatarstate_singleton", "2026_06_04_build_avatar_tracking_system_design_tailwind_css"], "relation": "form", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-04-build-avatar-tracking-system/design.md"}]}